---
import ServicePage from '../layouts/ServicePage.astro';

const canonical = 'https://www.mmseo.co.uk/privacy-policy/';
---

<ServicePage
  title="Privacy Policy | MM SEO"
  description="Privacy policy for mmseo.co.uk. How MM SEO collects, uses and protects your personal data in accordance with UK GDPR."
  canonical={canonical}
  breadcrumb="Privacy Policy"
>
  <section class="prose-section">
    <div class="container prose-container">

      <header class="prose-header">
        <p class="eyebrow">Legal</p>
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="prose-meta">Last updated: <time datetime="2026-04-13">13 April 2026</time></p>
      </header>

      <div class="prose">

        <h2>Who we are</h2>
        <p>This website is operated by <strong>MM SEO</strong>, a freelance SEO consultancy based in Marple, Stockport, UK. References to "we", "us" or "our" throughout this policy refer to MM SEO.</p>
        <p>If you have any questions about this policy, contact us at <a href="mailto:mithul.mistry@gmail.com">mithul.mistry@gmail.com</a>.</p>

        <h2>What data we collect and why</h2>

        <h3>Contact form</h3>
        <p>When you submit the enquiry form on this site we collect your <strong>name, email address, phone number (optional), website URL</strong> and any message you provide. We use this information solely to respond to your enquiry. Data submitted via the form is processed by <a href="https://web3forms.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Web3Forms</a> and forwarded to our email inbox. We do not store form submissions on our own servers.</p>
        <p><strong>Legal basis:</strong> Legitimate interests (responding to a business enquiry you initiated).</p>

        <h3>Analytics — Google Analytics 4 (GA4)</h3>
        <p>With your consent we use Google Analytics 4 to understand how visitors use this site (pages visited, time on site, traffic source). GA4 sets cookies and sends anonymised data to Google servers in the US. We have enabled IP anonymisation.</p>
        <p><strong>Legal basis:</strong> Consent (you can withdraw at any time via the cookie banner).</p>

        <h3>Advertising — Google Ads</h3>
        <p>With your consent we use the Google Ads tag (<code>AW-798334161</code>) to measure the effectiveness of our advertising campaigns and track conversions (e.g. form submissions). Google may use this data to show you relevant ads across the Google network.</p>
        <p><strong>Legal basis:</strong> Consent.</p>

        <h3>Behaviour analytics — Microsoft Clarity</h3>
        <p>With your consent we use Microsoft Clarity to record anonymised session replays and heatmaps to improve site usability. Clarity may collect mouse movements, clicks and scroll depth. No personally identifiable information is captured.</p>
        <p><strong>Legal basis:</strong> Consent.</p>

        <h2>Cookies and consent</h2>
        <p>On your first visit a cookie banner asks for your consent before any advertising or analytics cookies are set. We implement <strong>Google Consent Mode v2</strong>, which means Google's tags operate in a cookieless, privacy-safe mode until you grant consent. Your choice is saved in your browser's local storage and you can change it at any time by clearing your browser data or contacting us.</p>
        <p>The site does not set any cookies that require consent before you interact with the banner.</p>

        <h2>Third-party services</h2>
        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr><th>Service</th><th>Purpose</th><th>Data processed</th><th>Privacy policy</th></tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td>Google Analytics 4</td>
              <td>Site analytics</td>
              <td>Anonymised usage data</td>
              <td><a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google</a></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Google Ads</td>
              <td>Ad measurement</td>
              <td>Conversion events</td>
              <td><a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google</a></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Microsoft Clarity</td>
              <td>Heatmaps &amp; session recording</td>
              <td>Anonymised behaviour data</td>
              <td><a href="https://privacy.microsoft.com/en-gb/privacystatement" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Microsoft</a></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Web3Forms</td>
              <td>Contact form processing</td>
              <td>Name, email, phone, website, message</td>
              <td><a href="https://web3forms.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Web3Forms</a></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Cloudflare Pages</td>
              <td>Website hosting</td>
              <td>Server logs (IP, request data)</td>
              <td><a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/en-gb/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cloudflare</a></td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>

        <h2>Data retention</h2>
        <p>Enquiry emails are retained in our inbox for as long as needed to manage the client relationship, and deleted when no longer necessary. Google Analytics data is retained for 14 months (the minimum GA4 setting). We do not retain any other personal data on our own systems.</p>

        <h2>Your rights under UK GDPR</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Access</strong> the personal data we hold about you</li>
          <li><strong>Rectify</strong> inaccurate data</li>
          <li><strong>Erase</strong> your data ("right to be forgotten")</li>
          <li><strong>Restrict</strong> or <strong>object</strong> to processing</li>
          <li><strong>Withdraw consent</strong> at any time (this does not affect the lawfulness of processing before withdrawal)</li>
          <li><strong>Lodge a complaint</strong> with the Information Commissioner's Office (ICO) at <a href="https://ico.org.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ico.org.uk</a></li>
        </ul>
        <p>To exercise any of these rights, email us at <a href="mailto:mithul.mistry@gmail.com">mithul.mistry@gmail.com</a>. We will respond within 30 days.</p>

        <h2>Data transfers outside the UK</h2>
        <p>Some third-party services listed above (Google, Microsoft) transfer data to the United States. These transfers are covered by standard contractual clauses or adequacy decisions recognised under UK GDPR.</p>

        <h2>Children's privacy</h2>
        <p>This site is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children.</p>

        <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this policy from time to time. The "last updated" date at the top of this page will reflect any changes. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ServicePage>

<style>
  .prose-section {
    padding: 3rem 0 5rem;
  }

  .prose-container {
    max-width: 740px;
  }

  .prose-header {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .prose-header h1 {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.875rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #F8F7F2;
    margin: 0.25rem 0 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .prose-meta {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: rgba(248, 247, 242, 0.4);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ── Prose body ────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .prose {
    color: rgba(248, 247, 242, 0.75);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .prose h2 {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #F8F7F2;
    margin: 2.5rem 0 0.75rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
  }

  .prose h3 {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: rgba(248, 247, 242, 0.9);
    margin: 1.75rem 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .prose p {
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .prose ul {
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .prose li {
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .prose a {
    color: #FF6826;
    text-decoration: none;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .prose a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .prose code {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.875em;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.09);
    border-radius: 0.2rem;
    padding: 0.1em 0.35em;
    color: rgba(248, 247, 242, 0.85);
  }

  /* ── Table ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .prose table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .prose th {
    text-align: left;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: rgba(248, 247, 242, 0.55);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.625rem 0.75rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.10);
  }

  .prose td {
    padding: 0.625rem 0.75rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    vertical-align: top;
    color: rgba(248, 247, 242, 0.7);
  }

  .prose tr:last-child td {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .prose table, .prose thead, .prose tbody, .prose th, .prose td, .prose tr {
      display: block;
    }
    .prose thead { display: none; }
    .prose td {
      padding: 0.375rem 0;
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    .prose tr {
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
      padding: 0.75rem 0;
    }
  }
</style>
